  <title>WebKit2.WebContext::initialize-web-extensions</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
connect('initialize-web-extensions', function (webContext, ): void);
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>This signal is emitted when a new web process is about to be
launched. It signals the most appropriate moment to use
<link xref="WebKit2.WebContext.set_web_extensions_initialization_user_data"/>
and <link xref="WebKit2.WebContext.set_web_extensions_directory"/>.</p>
  <p>Since 2.4</p>
<terms>
<item>
<title><code>webContext</code></title>
<p>instance of <link xref="WebKit2.WebContext"/> that is emitting the signal</p>
</item>
